data.description: Your dollars go further here in Lakeland, FL at Copper Ridge! Home lives bigger than stated on county records and features: a large open living space w/ a wide open kitchen, comfortably -sized master bath, converted sound studio space (easy to re-convert) indoor security system, and built-in central vacuum system. The lot is an expansive 11,000+ sqft what includes a screened in pool/area, fruit trees, ample room for more parking or even a camper/RV pulling up to a gorgeous view of the ranch-like preserve to the rear that really gives the property a country feel. Unsure of roof age (inspection is recommended), but all other insurance items should pass your 4 point inspection no problem. Call now and schedule a showing!
